    <item>
      <title>特朗普说，在关税之后，“要酷”，补充说“美好的时光”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/trump-urges-calm-after-tariffs-imposed-says-great-time-to-buy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）敦促美国人保持冷静，并在周三继续进行投资，因为他的互惠关税达到了打击，这表明白宫正在密切监视对税款的市场反应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/trump-urges-calm-after-tariffs-imposed-says-great-time-to-buy</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Apr 2025 13:57:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国在债券上警告中国，押在债券中的“正常去杠杆化”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/bessent-sees-normal-deleveraging-in-bonds-warns-china-on-yuan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部长斯科特·贝斯特（Scott Bessent）在美国国库中抛弃了抛售，称没有系统性的作用，并且警告中国没有试图贬低其对美国关税远足的报复汇率的贬值。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/bessent-sees-normal-deleveraging-in-bonds-warns-china-on-yuan</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Apr 2025 12:05:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德克萨斯州野猫不耐烦，因为油价坦克</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/texas-wildcatters-grow-impatient-with-trump-as-oil-prices-tank</link>
      <description><![CDATA[二叠纪盆地石油协会在本周的“春摆”高尔夫锦标赛上的愤怒喃喃自语并不全是错过的推杆或失落的球。球道上的德克萨斯州油手们更加严重关注：他们选举的总统是油价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/texas-wildcatters-grow-impatient-with-trump-as-oil-prices-tank</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Apr 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券市场撤退，作为美国国债，全球范围</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/treasuries-fire-sale-sends-long-term-yields-soaring-worldwide</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自2020年大流行以来，美国国债的回调发出的长期收益率最高，随着投资者出售政府债券以筹集现金，金融动荡和流浪市场的避风港造成的损失加剧了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/treasuries-fire-sale-sends-long-term-yields-soaring-worldwide</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Apr 2025 05:24:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贸易交易谈判将股票提升，因为债券的卖出了：市场包装</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当财政部长斯科特·贝森特（Scott Bessent）说，他设想与美国盟友达成贸易协定时，股票在华尔街的另一个混乱日子开始弹跳，债券削减了抛售，这使人们担心美国会冒失去其天堂地位的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Apr 2025 22:34:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>皮博迪（Peabody</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/peabody-reviews-3-8-billion-coal-deal-after-anglo-mine-ignition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[皮博迪能源公司（Peabody Energy Corp.）股价上涨后，该公司表示正在审查一项价值高达37.8亿美元的交易，以在澳大利亚矿山发生大火后购买盎格鲁美国公司的钢铁制造煤炭业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/peabody-reviews-3-8-billion-coal-deal-after-anglo-mine-ignition</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Apr 2025 22:29:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者以快速的速度从石油熊基金中兑现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/investors-cash-out-of-oil-bear-fund-in-biggest-move-since-2020</link>
      <description><![CDATA[与石油市场相关的交易所买卖产品刚刚看到了自2020年以来最大的资金流出。原油价格跌至四年低点，一些投资者退出了该基金以兑现利润。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/investors-cash-out-of-oil-bear-fund-in-biggest-move-since-2020</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Apr 2025 20:23:11 GMT</pubDate>
